{"comments":"Persistence Atom — Behavior of values outside active duration.\n\nDescribes the thermodynamic/state behavior of a value when the driving\nforce (animation) is not active.\n\nThis replaces the legacy CSS concept of \"FillMode\".\n\n## States\n\n- **None** (Elastic): System returns to ground state (initial value).\n  Equivalent to CSS 'none'.\n\n- **PersistEnd** (Plastic): System retains the final high-energy state.\n  Equivalent to CSS 'forwards'.\n\n- **PersistStart** (Anticipatory): System assumes start state immediately\n  upon scheduling, before time T=0. Equivalent to CSS 'backwards'.\n\n- **PersistBoth** (Full): System is fully state-captured at both ends.\n  Equivalent to CSS 'both'.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[51,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Persistence.purs","start":[51,3]},"title":"None"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[52,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Persistence.purs","start":[52,3]},"title":"PersistEnd"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[53,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Persistence.purs","start":[53,3]},"title":"PersistStart"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[54,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Persistence.purs","start":[54,3]},"title":"PersistBoth"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Persistence"],"Persistence"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[56,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Persistence.purs","start":[56,1]},"title":"eqP